  _lines:
  - _speaker: 0
    _portrait: {fileID: 0}
    _dialogueText: Welcome to the Squirrel's Stash! We probably have what you're
      looking for.
  - _speaker: 1
    _portrait: {fileID: 0}
    _dialogueText: Can I have some flour?
  - _speaker: 0
    _portrait: {fileID: 0}
    _dialogueText: Sorry, flour's off-limits for now. This valuable product has been
      scarce since the wheat famine, so you'll need special access.
